These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-1::.
There are 2 different favourite colors: emerald, lavender
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: dubstep, reggae
1. the person who likes lavender is somewhere to the left of the fan of dubstep##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |
| Color           | lavender | emerald |
| Music-Genre   | reggae     | dubstep  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-2::.
House: cottage, farmhouse
The people use 2 different means of transport: airplane, motorbike
1. the person driving the airplane is somewhere to the left of the cottage house##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |     2     |
| House         | farmhouse   | cottage      |
| Transport   | airplane | motorbike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-3::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: r&b, rock
The people have 2 different jobs:  project-manager, pilot
1. the fan of r&b is somewhere to the right of the project-manager##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2    |
| Music-Genre   | rock | r&b    |
| Job     | project-manager | pilot |

